    <string name="faq_backup_restore">How to backup and restore data?</string>
    <string name="faq_backup_restore_answer">Go to \"Data Management\" in the \"Profile\" page to backup and restore your data. Backup files are saved in your phone storage and can be restored after reinstalling the app.</string>
    <string name="faq_theme_setting">How to change app theme?</string>
    <string name="faq_theme_setting_answer">Go to \"App Settings\" in the \"Profile\" page to choose between light, dark, or system theme.</string>
    <string name="faq_language_setting">How to change app language?</string>
    <string name="faq_language_setting_answer">Go to \"App Settings\" in the \"Profile\" page to choose between Chinese, English, or system language.</string>
    <string name="faq_notification">How to set up notifications?</string>
    <string name="faq_notification_answer">Go to \"App Settings\" in the \"Profile\" page to enable/disable notifications and set the advance reminder time.</string>
    <string name="faq_shift_template">How to use shift templates?</string>
    <string name="faq_shift_template_answer">When adding a shift, you can select from your saved templates to quickly fill in the information. You can also save the current shift as a new template.</string>

